public class Schedules
extends SspAction

Handle requests to schedules page.

The schedules page displays all currently available schdules and provides input forms to schedule new events.

getOption

protected String getOption(PortalBehavior pb,
                           HttpServletRequest request,
                           String selectedOptionId,

                    throws net.juniper.smgt.sae.sae.SAEException,
                           net.juniper.smgt.sae.sae.UnknownUserException
Extract an option from curent request from list of options.

This is a convenience method which gets the requested option from the request and exports both the list of options and the option itself through the request object.

Parameters:
pb - current Portal behavior
request - current request
selectedOptionId - The bean name for the selected option
optionsId - The bean name for the options
options - The list of options
Throws:
net.juniper.smgt.sae.sae.SAEException - If the requested option is not part of the list ov available options
net.juniper.smgt.sae.sae.UnknownUserException
